						<div class="postbody">See the <a href="http://nesdevwiki.org/index.php/APU_Pulse" class="postlink">pulse wave section of the Wiki</a>. For $4003 and $4007, it lists the side effects, including "The sequencer is restarted at the first value of the current sequence". Below that the sequences are shown. The workaround is complex, <a href="http://nesdev.com/bbs/viewtopic.php?t=231" class="postlink">using the sweep to change the high bits of the period</a> instead of setting it directly.</div>

